      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone looking for value over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior shows significant wear with some fading on the upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, though it has high mileage and will likely need a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
