      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. Every facet of this vehicle\u2014from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments\u2014demonstrates a level of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who accepts no compromises in quality or performance. We invite serious inquiries for this distinguished automotive specimen.",
